(119, 'Ayaka - Close Your Eyes (3 of 3)', 31, 315193, 16589, 16589106, 'Capture14.PNG', '5:55', '2020-05-25', '<p>From the songs recorded in Ayaka&#39;s first cover album and second studio album &quot;Yu-On Club ~ 1st grade ~&quot;, three&nbsp;songs have been converted into music videos.</p><p>These three MVs are not separate stories, but are original stories written so as to be a connected trilogy.</p><p>Browse order</p><p>Story1. In Between the Sky and You<br />Story2. LA &atilde;&fnof;&raquo; LA &atilde;&fnof;&raquo; LA LOVE SONG<br />Story3. Close Your Eyes</p><p>Screen writer: Makoto Zuiuch&Aring;&laquo;</p><p>Director: Kensaku Kakimoto<br /><br />In &quot;In Between the Sky and You&quot;, tells&nbsp;the childhood of Isamu, the main character of the story.<br />In &quot;LA LA LA LOVE SONG&quot;, tells how Isamu met&nbsp;Yuu, the second main character of the story.<br />In &quot;Close your eyes&quot;, tells how Isamu cope with Yuu&#39;s death.<br /><br />Ayaka herself appears at the key points of each story in a standing position as if she narrates the story.</p><p>(C) 2020 AstAtion / Timel', 5529702),
