(58, 'Beautiful Life, Beautiful Day (Treasure Chest OST Pt. 2) - Jimin, Jungkook, V', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16, 2, 'blbd.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12433887', '-', 0),
(59, 'Beautiful', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, 'beautiful.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12435422', '-', 0),
(60, 'The ReVe Festival (Deluxe)', 37, 4, 1, 0, 79600, 13, 2, 'reve-festival.jpg', 'Album', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12439314', 'Red Velvet has unleashed their dark, laid back debut album \'The ReVe Festival. Backed with heavy 80\'s inspiration, moody instrumentals and lyrics written by all members themselves, the album focuses in dark imagery of relationships, mere nostalgia and being one in sound.', 79600),
(61, 'Psycho', 37, 0, 0, 0, 0, 13, 2, 'psycho.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12440603', 'The title track of the album, \'Psycho\' brings out inspirations from orchestral arrangements, clinging onto an essential theme of a side in a relationship developing in toxicity and pain.\n', 0),
(62, 'The greatest', 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30, 'the-greatest.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12441008', '‘The greatest’ harks back to a different music era to what we live in today, and if it is indicative of the new album that is due imminently, it is sure to be a hit with fans and critics alike.', 0),
(63, 'Einstein', 33, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, 'einstein.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12448291', 'The most ‘Cookie-Cutter’ song on the album in structure and vibe is more funk in sound. It features a very “Bennie and the Jets” type sound in melody, but more disco-fied. Harry speaks of growing up and achieving high grades in school, creating a metaphor by comparing working for grades to please your parents to working to complete an album to please fans, singing in a Stevie Wonder-high energy style. Harry cites himself as an “Einstein at work “ while working his craft. ', 0),
(64, 'Convicted Lover', 27, 0, 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'convicted-lover.jpg', 'Single', '2020-04-27', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12466579', 'Convicted Loverâ€™ is the official lead single off of PC music singer Charli XCXâ€™s new debut studio album. Focusing on her transcendence from the typical, the energetic SOPHIE-produced track articulates Charliâ€™s frustration with ordinary relationships.', 0),
