(73, 'UN2VERSE', 38, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 13, 'un2verse.jpg', 'Album', '2020-05-01', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12495569', 'Un2verse is the first album by American-South Korean rapper and singer, Jessi. It was released on May 1, 2020 by Timeless Music and distributed by Interscope Records/UMG Recordings Inc. It consists of twelve songs, all written by the singer, two produced by her, and includes collaborations with rappers Changmo, Year of the Ox, and Japanese singer/labelmate Ayaka. \"Ssenunni\" was released as the leading single.', 0),
