(77, 'Mariners Apartment Complex', 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19, 30, 'mac.png', 'Single', '2020-05-06', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12526967', 'The song is a mid tempo, band driven collaboration between Lana Del Rey and Jack Antonoff, who is the executive producer of her forthcoming record. Lasting four minutes and six seconds, it has country elements, merged classic rock and psychedelic rock, and is the first love-themed song released from the record, even if it has sad undertones that are most present in the verses.', 0);
