(73, 'UN2VERSE', 38, 9, 1, 15, 74000, 1, 13, 'un2verse.jpg', 'Album', '2020-05-01', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12495569', 'Un2verse is the first album by American-South Korean rapper and singer, Jessi. It was released on May 1, 2020 by Timeless Music and distributed by Interscope Records/UMG Recordings Inc. It consists of twelve songs, all written by the singer, two produced by her, and includes collaborations with rappers Changmo, Year of the Ox, and Japanese singer/labelmate Ayaka. \"Ssenunni\" was released as the leading single.', 74000),
(74, 'GUCCI', 38, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 13, 'un2verse.jpg', 'Single', '2020-05-01', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12495590', '--', 0),
(75, 'Blank Space', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 2, 'blank-space.jpg', 'Single', '2020-05-03', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12502806', '\"Blank Space\" is an electropop song that makes fun of Swift\'s recent exposure in the media about her dating life, portraying herself as \"an overly attached man-eater who dates for songwriting material\".', 0),
(76, 'Never Really Over', 40, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 2, 'never-really-over.jpg', 'Single', '2020-05-04', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12513673', '\"Never Really Over\" is an electropop song that contains a house beat, solely written by Katy.\n', 0),
(77, 'Mariners Apartment Complex', 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19, 30, 'mac.png', 'Single', '2020-05-06', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12526967', 'The song is a mid tempo, band driven collaboration between Lana Del Rey and Jack Antonoff, who is the executive producer of her forthcoming record. Lasting four minutes and six seconds, it has country elements, merged classic rock and psychedelic rock, and is the first love-themed song released from the record, even if it has sad undertones that are most present in the verses.', 0),
(78, 'Telephone', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 'telephone.jpg', 'Single', '2020-05-09', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12550366', '--', 0),
(79, 'Norman Fucking Rockwell', 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19, 30, 'nfr.png', 'Album', '2020-05-09', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12544693', 'The album that the world has been waiting for is finally here. Boasting fourteen tracks, and conceived over eighteen months in sunny California with long-time friend Jack Antonoff, the record harks back to classic psychedelic rock and it’s finest, spawning mega hit “The greatest”, and new fan favourite “Mariners Apartment Complex”, both of which have dominated the charts as of late.', 0),
(80, 'Roman Holiday', 18, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 30, 'roman-holiday.jpg', 'Single', '2020-05-09', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12544708', 'The song, entitled “Roman Holiday”, is a mid-tempo contemporary pop-rock track that is themed around a struggling relationship, and focuses on the irony of her and her partner’s differing perspectives regarding the love. ', 0),
