(16, 'Raini on Me (ft Raini Rodriguez & Rihanna) - Remix', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 6, 21, 'rom-remix.png', 'Single', '2020-03-24', 'https://gagadaily.com/forums/topic/319051-create-a-label-x/?do=findComment&comment=12230085', '', 0),
